<h1 className={"openapi__heading"}>Delete lookup list</h1>

<MethodEndpoint method={"delete"} path={"/v1/lookup-lists/{id}"}></MethodEndpoint>



Deletes a lookup list. Note that this action can affect rules, dashboards, and reports if they are dependent on the lookup list. 
Please ensure to change the region in the URL to match your account's region.
